---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section>
    <h2>About Prompt Loop</h2>
    <p><strong>Prompt Loop</strong> is an AI-powered skill development app that helps you build expertise faster through deliberate practice loops. The app provides intelligent feedback and structured learning paths to accelerate your growth.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>How it works</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Start a practice session in your chosen skill domain</li>
        <li>Complete structured exercises designed for deliberate practice</li>
        <li>Receive AI-powered feedback on your performance</li>
        <li>Track your progress and see improvement over time</li>
        <li>Adaptive learning adjusts difficulty based on your level</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>About this website</h3>
      <p>This site is built with Astro and provides documentation for the Prompt Loop app. The source is in <code>/astro</code> and deploys to GitHub Pages when a release is published.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
